class Solution {
    public int majorityElement(int[] nums) {
        int count=1;
        int n=nums.length;
        int ele=nums[0];
        for(int i=1;i<n;i++)
        {
            if(count==0)
              ele=nums[i];
            if(ele==nums[i])
             count++;
             else
             count--;
        }
        return ele;
    }
}

## Complexity
**Time Complexity:** 
o(n) only for loop.

**Space Complexity:**
0(1)
